37
00:02:37,031 --> 00:02:38,950
[NARRATOR] This is the time
known as the Great Pirate Era.

38
00:02:38,983 --> 00:02:40,618
A countless array of pirates

39
00:02:40,652 --> 00:02:43,154
go to battle across the seas
in search of the One Piece,

40
00:02:43,188 --> 00:02:45,456
the legendary
treasure left behind

41
00:02:45,490 --> 00:02:47,825
by Gold Roger,
King of the Pirates.

42
00:02:47,859 --> 00:02:50,695
Monkey D. Luffy, a boy
whose body turned to rubber

43
00:02:50,728 --> 00:02:52,530
after eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,

44
00:02:52,564 --> 00:02:55,433
sets sail to become
the next King of the Pirates.

45
00:02:55,466 --> 00:02:58,136
As Luffy and his crew
conquer numerous obstacles

46
00:02:58,169 --> 00:02:59,804
they capture the
unwanted attention

47
00:02:59,837 --> 00:03:01,472
of the World Government,

48
00:03:01,506 --> 00:03:05,109
which will use any means
necessary to stop them.

49
00:03:05,143 --> 00:03:08,046
