Now this is exciting!

50
00:03:08,079 --> 00:03:11,416
I can't wait to see what
kind of adventure's up next!

51
00:03:11,449 --> 00:03:14,686
[NARRATOR] With a charted course
awash in danger and intrigue.

52
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:16,020
The crew will cut a path

53
00:03:16,054 --> 00:03:19,624
across the Grand Line
to the New World!

54
00:03:22,594 --> 00:03:24,529
[NARRATOR] After being
separated from his crew,

55
00:03:24,562 --> 00:03:27,031
Luffy set out to rescue
his captured brother, Ace.

56
00:03:27,065 --> 00:03:31,035
To do so, he snuck into the
government prison, Impel Down.

57
00:03:31,069 --> 00:03:33,204
Along the way, he ran
into Buggy the Clown,

58
00:03:33,238 --> 00:03:36,808
as well as Mr. 3,
a former Baroque Works agent.

59
00:03:36,841 --> 00:03:40,845
Together, they descended into
the depths of the prison.

60
00:03:40,878 --> 00:03:43,948
[MR. 3] This is Level 3,
The Starvation Hell.

61
00:03:43,982 --> 00:03:47,752
In other words, let's move while
we have the sweat to spare.

62
00:03:47,785 --> 00:03:50,622
Okay. Then let's go
to Level 4 already.

63
00:03:50,655 --> 00:03:51,556
[MR. 3, BUGGY]
Seriously?

64
00:03:51,589 --> 00:03:53,758
[SPHINX]
Spaghetti.

65
00:03:53,791 --> 00:03:55,960
[LEVEL 3 GUARD 431C]
The Sphinx is awake!

66
00:03:55,994 --> 00:03:59,931
[SPHINX]
Deep fried noodles!

67
00:03:59,964 --> 00:04:04,168
Gum-Gum. Gatling!

68
00:04:05,136 --> 00:04:06,771
[NARRATOR]
Meanwhile, Boa Hancock,

69
00:04:06,804 --> 00:04:09,173
who helped Luffy
break into Impel Down,

70
00:04:09,207 --> 00:04:10,808
drew ever closer to the floor

71
00:04:10,842 --> 00:04:13,711
where Ace is
being held prisoner.

72
00:04:13,745 --> 00:04:17,649
[BON CLAY]
♪ Un. Deux. Ora!

73
00:04:17,682 --> 00:04:19,917
Hey. Who's that singing?

74
00:04:21,552 --> 00:04:25,056
[BON CLAY]
♪ Un. Deux. Ora!

75
00:04:25,089 --> 00:04:28,593
♪ Un. Deux. Krah!

76
00:04:28,626 --> 00:04:31,796
♪ Un. Deux. Ora!

77
00:04:31,829 --> 00:04:34,032
[MR. 3 yells]

78
00:04:36,834 --> 00:04:38,036
