"The Unleashed Swan!

79
00:04:38,069 --> 00:04:40,338
A Reunion with Bon Clay!"

80
00:04:44,208 --> 00:04:47,011
[BON CLAY]
♪ Oh, come my way!

81
00:04:47,045 --> 00:04:50,715
♪ Oh-Oh-Oh, come my way!

82
00:04:50,748 --> 00:04:51,949
♪ Yeah, Yeah!

83
00:04:51,983 --> 00:04:54,285
♪ Oh, come my way!

84
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:55,353
♪ Yeah, Yeah!

85
00:04:55,386 --> 00:04:57,121
[BUGGY panting] I can
barely stand in this heat,

86
00:04:57,155 --> 00:04:58,556
but that guy's singing

87
00:04:58,589 --> 00:05:01,292
like he's at somebody's
birthday party.

88
00:05:01,326 --> 00:05:04,595
If he's a prisoner here,
he must be tough as hell.

89
00:05:04,629 --> 00:05:08,199
[MR. 3 panting]

90
00:05:08,232 --> 00:05:11,569
[MR. 3] I know this voice.
I know this song.

91
00:05:11,602 --> 00:05:15,106
Hey, partner. I think
this guy can help us out.

92
00:05:16,341 --> 00:05:19,544
[MR. 3] Wait! What?
Let's discuss this first!

93
00:05:21,612 --> 00:05:23,715
[BON CLAY]
♪ Oh, come my way!

94
00:05:23,748 --> 00:05:24,716
♪ Spin! Spin!

95
00:05:24,749 --> 00:05:27,819
♪ Oh, come my way!

96
00:05:27,852 --> 00:05:29,887
Keep it up, boys!

97
00:05:29,921 --> 00:05:31,022
♪ Spin and spin

98
00:05:31,055 --> 00:05:34,025
♪ like you're caught up
in the tide of the times! ♪

99
00:05:34,058 --> 00:05:35,860
Hurry! This way!

100
00:05:35,893 --> 00:05:36,994
Wait! Listen.

101
00:05:37,028 --> 00:05:39,230
I don't think... we should.

102
00:05:39,263 --> 00:05:41,232
